snippet.title: [Official Audio] PEtER & Dozin - Holy disco
snippet.description:
☑ 신청곡은 커뮤니티 댓글로 적어주세요  ▶https://www.youtube.com/@kbsmediamusicplus/community

완벽한 인간을 원하는
세상의 소리에 지친 나.
닫힌 문 앞에 멈춰선 나.

그 속에서 
조용히 들려오는 작은 속삭임, 
GOOD NEWS.
“겁내지 말고, 조용히 귀 기울여봐."
I get my D.I.S.C.O.

[Credit]

Lyrics by Rockepunch(Aiming), PEtER, Dozin
Composed by Rockepunch(Aiming), PEtER, Suji Park
Arranged by Rockepunch(Aiming)
Vocal by PEtER & Dozin
Piano by Rockepunch(Aiming)
Bass by Rockepunch(Aiming)
Recorded by 유형석 @Wave Studio
Mixed and Mastered by Rockepunch(Aiming)

Executive Producer Suji Park
Album Artwork Jungho Han, Suji Park
M/V & Video Art Director Jungho Han
Choreography by ONEW, PEtER
Japanses Translation By BiTL


#KBS미디어뮤직플러스 #KBSMEDIAMUSICPLUS #케이비에스미디어뮤직플러스 #PEtER #Dozin
